headline: Freeport Provides Update on PT Freeport Indonesia Operations
summary: PHOENIX, October 06, 2025--Freeport (NYSE: FCX) announced today an update on the search for the remaining five team members who were missing following the previously reported September 8 mud rush incident at the Grasberg Block Cave mine in Indonesia.
